OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBA halts sales of          
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fshort-haul tickets from    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5FHeathrow                   
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, British Airways has halted sales of    
OL,6, tickets on short-haul flights from     
OL,7, Heathrow Airport until 8 August as     
OL,8, disruption to air travel continues.    
OL,10,FThe move is due to the cap on daily    
OL,11,Fpassenger numbers that the UK's largest
OL,12,Fairport has imposed over the summer.   
OL,14,FThe sales suspension will affect BA's  
OL,15,Fflights to domestic and European       
OL,16,Fdestinations.                          
OL,18,FThousands of air travellers have been  
OL,19,Fhit by disruption in recent weeks,     
OL,20,Fincluding last-minute cancellations.   
